        "created_at": "2025-09-03T17:40:37.777Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi, I’ve recently gone through the same process and wrote a detailed step-by-step guide on deploying the latest Signal Server:<br>\n<a href=\"https://blog.iriyanto.com/self-deploy-the-latest-version-of-signal-server-v2025082200?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Self-deploy the latest version of Signal Server v2025082200</a></p>\n<p>There, I explain how to configure server.yml and secrets-bundle.yml for minimal requirements (no payments, device checks, etc.) with Redis and DynamoDB-Local via Docker.</p>\n<p>If you don’t want to bother with the hassle of doing it yourself, you can also contact me for setup and consulting services.</p>\n<p>Hope this helps!</p>",
